Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是忍者联军之术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可悲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怀揣的希望根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今 他们也将一并不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾差不多该出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五杜门 开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不是针对十尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是针对我们发动的攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 擒贼先擒王是基本常识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把控制十尾的他俩干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想得手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先阻止十尾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾不是被封住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩部的骨头脱臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 感知水球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直堪比小行星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾方才并非我们所阻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是为了变身蓄力才一动不动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能阻止这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 根本奈何不了他俩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此也要阻止它 否则我们就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓尿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其害怕 还不如积蓄些查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便随时配合总部下达的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须先封锁十尾的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则无法攻击控制它的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怎么才能封锁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我族最擅长的束缚敌人的术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用在那种庞然大物上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便消耗再多的查克拉 效果也微乎其微
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亥一 快联络卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据你刚刚汇报的一系列情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想确认一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.35,0:04:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾越来越难控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用柱间的细胞加强束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种状态下的十尾究竟拥有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不想确认一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何为绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角先生 暂且中断一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角大人 亥一大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 神威根本来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用土遁抬高它的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然可以攻击这么远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的尾兽根本不是一个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才射了一发就开始摇晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来控制得还不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么远的城镇 一瞬间就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才起就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它似乎专门攻击远处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 所有的城镇和人都在射程范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在避难的大名以及留守村子的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有各国的普通居民都有危险了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上的忍者们 正是为了保护他们而战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想断了我们的信念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 青大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好本职工作即可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最后的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络战场上的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了阻止十尾的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来 联军的指挥部就摧毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本常识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按照父亲所说的去做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是作战胜利的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿角大叔和亥一大叔他们到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次 你向右回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八卦掌回天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是战场 现在正在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难免有人员伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 作战计划失败的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸和井野的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会说“逝于子前乃忍者所愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我的父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你的力量在作战中不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了战斗的顺利 无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都要保护鸣人君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 日向乃木叶最强一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想在他们大言不惭之前发动攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但十尾不是很好控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前这个形态还能支撑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成为人柱力就无法控制十尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我成为十尾的人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这具秽土转生的尸身可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须是有生命的血肉之躯才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生的你就喜欢拉人同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没不惜自爆地用尾兽球攻击脚下的联军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你怕我也成为炮灰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了成为人柱力 必须真正复活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:10:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就需要我舍身对你施展轮回天生术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在正处在不得不对我言听计从的微妙立场上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年的小兔崽子 翅膀也变硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打从一开始 我就没当你是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后的一切就由你决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让他们彻底知道何谓绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木遁.扦插之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在九尾的力量恢复之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的山土术应该可以抵挡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 凝聚查克拉需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太多了 回天应付不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功变成仙人模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能光依靠你这个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螺旋手里剑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八卦空壁掌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 被瞄准了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅靠雏田和宁次的空掌…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土遁.山土之术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医疗班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿 这里有重伤者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田大小姐可以为你而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 我的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也成为其中之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能死在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是对日向一族…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然记得你把曾经的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从命运的诅咒中解救出来的那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜失去生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称我为天才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我不一样 不是拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为了保护同伴而选择死亡的那种自由感受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说“绝不会让同伴受到伤害”吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让同伴受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的那句“绝不会让同伴受到伤害”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 看看四周 再说一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种再说一次试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触摸同伴逐渐冰冷的身躯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切实地感受一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日差 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来这种事还会继续
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那幼稚的话语和理念都会变为虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是空谈理想和希望的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 这种现实还值得留恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲和母亲不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父自来也也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 只要你继续和我对立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴将会一个接一个逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界不会再有认可你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后等待你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你最熟悉 最恐怖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直和原来的我如出一辙呢 带土
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人过不了多久就会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想摧毁联军的核心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必存在于这种现实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该过来了吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才宁次哥哥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“鸣人的命不止一条”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让同伴受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话和你的信念都不是虚无啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次哥哥记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并诠释了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止是鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这番话语和信念牢记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相支撑并连接着彼此的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这样才是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大家舍弃了这番话语和信念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次哥哥所做的一切就毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真的杀害自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断和同伴的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我们一起站起来吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 雏田大小姐可以为你而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 你的命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…不止一条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘了老夫也在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会斩断羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会舍弃同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可实际上 宁次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续啰嗦试试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我打爆你 然后占据你的身体 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母在你刚出生不久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也做过和宁次相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不惜牺牲自己 将作为敌人的老夫封印在你的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把未来托付于你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的命打一出生 就已经和那两条命紧密相连了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不采取任何行动 非要等鸣人的反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你十分在意鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么干不仅十尾会受伤 连你也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十尾的表皮很坚韧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎瞄准了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充电完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请小心 蜂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万万不要乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需担心 守护联军 由我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命早就不止一条了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雏田 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有你在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的手 宽大有力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上吧 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人非常安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走来 很多同伴我都无力保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在牢笼里只能等死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是绝佳的暗喻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就像刚才那个枉死的小鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次的意志永不泯灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.37,0:22:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐并活跃着的人们
